    <summary>Secure P2P chat in the terminal</summary>
    <description>
t-chat is a secure peer-to-peer chat application for the terminal.

## Features
- Zero configuration - no servers to deploy
- End-to-end encryption (ChaCha20-Poly1305)
- Direct P2P connection via UDP hole punching
- Works across the internet without port forwarding

## Usage
```
t-chat create -u yourname -p password    # Create a session
t-chat join SESSION_CODE -u name -p pass # Join a session
```
    </description>
